# 📊 Kommo-o - Data Format Converter CLI

Convert between JSON, YAML, TOML, CSV, XML instantly.

## 🧠 Problem

**This project solves:**
- Config files in different formats everywhere
- Manual copying/pasting to online converters
- No command-line tool that handles all formats
- Data migration between tools requires manual work

## 💡 Features

**List the main capabilities:**
- Convert between all popular formats
- Validate syntax
- Pretty-print with indentation
- Extract paths with dot notation (`data.users[0].name`)
- Merge multiple files
- Command piping (stdin/stdout)
- Quiet mode for scripts

## 🧩 Advanced Features

- Environment variable substitution
- Template rendering
- Diff between versions
- Validation against schemas

## 🧭 Roadmap

**V1 (MVP):**
- JSON, YAML, TOML, CSV conversion
